      "content": "exactly. it's like there's nowhere to go from here. people say \"it gets better\" or \"start over,\" but how do you start over when your entire reputation is a crater? the damage is permanent. i look at the future and i just see a long, empty stretch of being hated or pitied. i don't see a way to actually be a person again. it just feels like the end of the road, honestly.",
